Privacy Policy for SheWords

SheWords does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data.

All text processing is performed locally within the user's browser. The extension reads webpage content only to perform word replacement based on predefined or user-defined rules.

No data is sent to any external servers, and no user activity is tracked.

The extension does not use cookies, analytics, or any third-party tracking technologies.

